<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>FinTrack</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      h2 {
        color: #1976d2;
      }
      table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      th, td {
        padding: 10px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Hi {{firstName}},</h2>
      <p>This is a reminder that you have upcoming bills due. Please make sure to pay them on time to avoid any late fees.</p>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Bill Name</th>
            <th>Amount</th>
            <th>Due Date</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {{#each billings}}
            <tr>
              <td>{{this.name}}</td>
              <td>{{this.amount}}</td>
              <td>{{this.dueDate}}</td>
            </tr>
          {{/each}}
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <p>If youâ€™ve already paid these bills, please ignore this message.</p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Thank you,<br/>Your Finance Tracker Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
